libsource.description:
Multi connection point. Often used as Generic Header-pin footprint for 0.1 inch spaced/style header connections You can populate with any combo of single row headers, but if you'd like an exact match, check these:
  • Header - 2x3 (Male, 0.1") (PRT-12807)
  • Header - 2x3 (Female, 0.1") (PRT-13010)
  • 2x3 Pin Shrouded Header (PRT-10877)
On any of the 0.1 inch spaced packages, you can populate with these:
  • Break Away Headers - Straight (PRT-00116)
  • Break Away Male Headers - Right Angle (PRT-00553)
  • Female Headers (PRT-00115)
  • Break Away Headers - Machine Pin (PRT-00117)
  • Break Away Female Headers - Swiss Machine Pin (PRT-00743)
Special note: the shrouded connector mates well with our 3x2 ribbon cables:
  • Ribbon Crimp Connector - 6-pin (2x3, Female) (PRT-10651)
  • Ribbon Cable - 6 wire (15ft) (PRT-10646)
20V Vds, 0.63 Id, N-Channel MOSFET with ESD protection, SOT-523
Push button switch, generic, two pins
Push button switch, generic, two pins
1A Low Dropout regulator, positive, 5.0V fixed output, SOT-223
Analog temperature sensor, NTC, 0.3C accuracy, -8.2mV/C, -50C to +150C, 1.8 to 5.5V, SC-70-5
